Class NodeData

  • java.lang.Object
    • api.NodeData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    node_data, java.lang.Comparable<node_data>
    public class NodeData
extends java.lang.Object
implements node_data, java.lang.Comparable<node_data>
    This class represents the set of operations applicable on a node (vertex) in a directed weighted graph.
